{{Otheruses|jewel}}
'''Jewel-fruit''' grew on [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]] and, along with a type of seaweed also native to the world, was used to make a type of candy enjoyed by [[Vergere]]. It was also one of the many fruits distilled to make ''[[Tihaar/Legends|Tihaar]]''.

